If you have questions or comments, leave them there for us and we'll be in touch very soon.
如果你有问题或评论，请留在那里，我们会很快联系你。

173
00:10:28,880 --> 00:10:29,880
All right, we'll see you guys there.
好了，我们到时候见。

174
